{"tid":1779781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警世: 請停止在twitter攻擊美國左膠. 美國民主黨幫左香港唔少.","createTime":"2019-12-12T01:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T02:15:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"643e48aa33b45bd37928aed2a89e6f49f4c03d79","tid":1779781,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:50:16.000Z","msg":"見到有人開始係twitter借trump兒子撐香港言論攻擊美國左膠, 甚至攻擊american liberal, 仲要用英文寫.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係想講, 香港人不應介入美國既政黨之爭與左右之爭. 而且,&nbsp; 美國民主黨幫左香港唔少.<br />\n- 民主黨主導既眾議院, 香港法案都可以極快通過.<br />\n- 美國民主黨既參議院黨團, 不斷摧促盡快審議香港法案.<br />\n- 民主黨議會大佬如Nancy Pelosi, Chuck Schumer都係力撐香港.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>反中共係不分左中右</strong><br />\nSolomon Yue 身為共和黨大佬, 都唔係叫香港人支持共和黨, 而係叫香港人不要介入美國兩黨鬥爭.  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1695914/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1695914/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/2DwXvot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DwXvot.jpg&h=2e328b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSolomon Yue 提哂水, 大家要醒水.  要反左膠, 頂多係連登講就好, 唔好係twitter講."},{"pid":"5fe61617167035d3b06044eeeb2a0f579a441758","tid":1779781,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"警世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f214fa05e59b2c86a8aae4f94f5f395a0872e275","tid":1779781,"uid":163865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:51:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb97ea1b8cb575320e78a93ae2c72a91066f93e2","tid":1779781,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f214fa05e59b2c86a8aae4f94f5f395a0872e275","tid":1779781,"uid":163865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:51:05.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=